## DESCRIPTION
## Calculus 2, Given a pair of parametric equations, find the slope of the tangent line at some point t=a, determine the concavity at t=a.
## ENDDESCRIPTION


## DBsubject(Calculus - single variable)
## DBchapter(Parametric)
